---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout 
  title="Fabric Technology | Yilong Medical Scrubs - OEKO-TEX Certified" 
  description="Yilong's three-tier fabric system: Premium 205 GSM, Standard 180 GSM, Lightweight 130 GSM. OEKO-TEX certified. Lab-tested wash durability. Antibacterial & water-repellent options."
  keywords="medical scrubs fabric, 4-way stretch hospital uniform, OEKO-TEX fabric, scrub fabric technology, healthcare apparel textile"
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-slate-900 text-white py-16 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1 bg-secondary/20 border border-secondary/30 text-secondary text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-4">Core Technology</div>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-black mb-4">Fabric Technology</h1>
      <p class="text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">Three decades of fabric formula refinement. Three performance tiers engineered for different global markets. Every yarn tested for OEKO-TEX safety.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Fabric Introduction -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-6 text-slate-900">Built for Healthcare. Tested by Time.</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed">Yilong uses proprietary high-density 4-way stretch medical fabric formulas. Developed over 30 years, our three-tier system covers everything from premium D2C brands to budget-conscious hospital procurement.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- Fabric Comparison Table -->
      <div class="overflow-x-auto mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <table class="w-full text-sm md:text-base min-w-[700px]">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-slate-900 text-white">
              <th class="py-4 px-5 text-left font-black">Fabric Tier</th>
              <th class="py-4 px-5 text-left font-black">Composition</th>
              <th class="py-4 px-5 text-left font-black">Weight (GSM)</th>
              <th class="py-4 px-5 text-left font-black">Feel</th>
              <th class="py-4 px-5 text-left font-black">Best For</th>
              <th class="py-4 px-5 text-left font-black">Price Level</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="divide-y divide-slate-200">
            <tr class="bg-slate-50">
              <td class="py-4 px-5 font-black text-secondary">Premium Series</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-5">72% Polyester / 21% Rayon / 7% Spandex</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-5 font-bold">205 GSM</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-5">Ultra-soft, silky drape</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-5">USA / Canada brands, D2C, ecommerce sellers</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-5">$$$</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="py-4 px-5 font-black text-secondary">Standard Series</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-5">Polyester / Spandex blend</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-5 font-bold">180 GSM</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-5">Comfortable, durable</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-5">Hospital groups, clinics, distributors</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-5">$$</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="bg-slate-50">
              <td class="py-4 px-5 font-black text-secondary">Lightweight Series</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-5">Polyester / Spandex blend</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-5 font-bold">130 GSM</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-5">Lightweight, breathable</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-5">Philippines, Middle East, Africa, South America</td>
              <td class="py-4 px-5">$</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>
      <p class="text-center text-xs text-slate-400">P = Polyester (durability) · R = Rayon (softness, moisture absorption) · SP = Spandex (4-way stretch, recovery)</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- OEKO-TEX Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-green-50 border-y border-green-200">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-8">
        <div class="flex-shrink-0 text-center">
          <div class="w-20 h-20 bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-3 text-3xl font-black">✓</div>
          <p class="text-xs font-bold text-green-700 uppercase tracking-wider">Certified</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black mb-3 text-slate-900">OEKO-TEX® Standard 100 Certified</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">All Yilong fabrics are OEKO-TEX® Standard 100 certified — independently tested by authorized laboratories to ensure no harmful substances are present. Every fabric batch used in production carries current certification. Safe for prolonged skin contact, even in high-sweat healthcare environments.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Wash Test Data -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-10 md:mb-12">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-4 text-slate-900">Wash Durability — Lab Tested</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-500">Premium 205 GSM fabric tested by independent third-party laboratory. Results verified by SGS.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200">
            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-2">20x</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">After 20 Machine Washes</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black">✓</span> No fabric deformation or shrinkage</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black">✓</span> Color fastness rating: Grade 4 (good)</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black">✓</span> 4-way stretch recovery: >95%</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black">✓</span> No pilling visible</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200">
            <div class="text-4xl font-black text-secondary mb-2">40x</div>
            <h3 class="font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">After 40 Machine Washes</h3>
            <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-600 text-sm">
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black">✓</span> Fabric strength retention: >90%</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black">✓</span> No significant color fading</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black">✓</span> Seam integrity maintained</li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2"><span class="text-green-500 font-black">✓</span> Elastic recovery still >85%</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 mt-6 text-center">* Lab tests conducted by SGS-certified testing facility. Full test report available upon request with bulk order.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Functional Fabric Options -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-10 md:mb-12">
          <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest rounded-full mb-4">Optional Add-Ons</div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-4 text-slate-900">Functional Fabric Treatments</h2>
          <p class="text-slate-500">Upgrade your fabric with specialized treatments for specific healthcare environments. Available on most styles with MOQ requirements.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-300 transition">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl">🦠</span>
              <h3 class="font-black text-lg text-slate-900">Antibacterial Finishing</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">Silver ion antibacterial treatment inhibits bacterial growth on fabric surface. Ideal for high-infection-risk environments: ER, ICU, surgery departments.</p>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-secondary">Min. 200 sets per order · Surcharge applies</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-300 transition">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl">💧</span>
              <h3 class="font-black text-lg text-slate-900">Water-Repellent Finish</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">DWR (Durable Water Repellent) treatment repels fluids and liquids. Essential for surgery, emergency, and neonatal units where bodily fluid exposure is common.</p>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-secondary">Min. 200 sets per order · Surcharge applies</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-300 transition">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl">💨</span>
              <h3 class="font-black text-lg text-slate-900">Moisture-Wicking</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">Enhanced moisture transport technology moves sweat away from skin to fabric surface for rapid evaporation. Critical for hot climates, long shifts, and high-activity healthcare roles.</p>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-secondary">Available on all fabric tiers · Min. 100 sets</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 hover:border-blue-300 transition">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <span class="text-3xl">👔</span>
              <h3 class="font-black text-lg text-slate-900">Anti-Wrinkle Treatment</h3>
            </div>
            <p class="text-slate-600 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-3">Reduces fabric wrinkling after washing for a consistently neat appearance. Ideal for environments where professional presentation is paramount.</p>
            <p class="text-xs font-bold text-secondary">Available on all fabric tiers · Min. 100 sets</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center mt-8">
          <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-4">Functional treatments require minimum order quantities. Contact us for specific pricing per treatment type.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-secondary text-white font-bold px-8 py-3 rounded-full hover:bg-emerald-700 transition shadow-md">Request Functional Fabric Quote</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- 4-Way Stretch -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-20 bg-white border-t border-slate-100">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black mb-6 text-slate-900">What is 4-Way Stretch?</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">4-way stretch means the fabric stretches in both directions — lengthwise and crosswise — providing maximum freedom of movement. Healthcare professionals bend, lift, reach, and crouch throughout long shifts. Yilong's 4-way stretch scrubs move with the body, reducing fatigue and increasing comfort.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 text-center">
          <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl">
            <div class="text-2xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">↑↓</div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Vertical Stretch</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl">
            <div class="text-2xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">←→</div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Horizontal Stretch</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-6 bg-slate-50 rounded-2xl">
            <div class="text-2xl font-black text-secondary mb-1">⟳</div>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-500">Instant Recovery</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="py-12 md:py-16 bg-slate-900 text-white text-center">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-black mb-4">Have Questions About Our Fabrics?</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-400 max-w-lg mx-auto mb-6">Request fabric swatches or talk to our technical team. We will help you choose the right fabric for your target market.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-secondary text-white font-bold px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-emerald-700 transition shadow-lg">Request Fabric Swatches & Quote</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
